1. *Hram* je impozantan objekat. (The *temple* is an impressive building.)
2. Vernici su otišli u *hram* da se mole. (The believers went to the *temple* to pray.)
3. Građevinski radnici obnavljaju *hram*. (Construction workers are renovating the *temple*.)
4. Nalazimo se u blizini *hr*ama u Egiptu. (We are near the *temples* in Egypt.)
5. Praznik se održava u velikom *hramu*. (The holiday is held in the large *temple*.)
6. Svećenik stoji ispred *hr*ama i poziva ljude da uđu. (The priest is standing in front of the *temples* and inviting people to enter.)
7. Ovaj *hram* posvećen je boginji Athene. (This *temple* is dedicated to the goddess Athena.)
8. Posetili smo *hram* u Nepalu. (We visited a *temple* in Nepal.)
9. Arheolozi su pronašli ostatke starog *hr*ama. (Archaeologists found remains of an old *temple*.)
10. *Hramovi* u Grčkoj su impresivni zbog svoje arhitekture. (*Temples* in Greece are impressive because of their architecture.)

Note: In Serbian language, the word "hram" means temple or shrine, a place of worship.